HEADWORD: Atheize
<hw>A"the*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To render
atheistic or godless.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They endeavored to <qex>atheize</qex> one another.</q>
<rj><qau>Berkeley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
